4) Backend — muhim modul va kod ssenariylari (qisqacha namunalar)
4.1 main.py — FastAPI + WebSocket
python
Copy code
from fastapi import FastAPI, WebSocket, WebSocketDisconnect
from app.websocket_manager import ConnectionManager

app = FastAPI()
manager = ConnectionManager()

@app.websocket("/ws")
async def websocket_endpoint(ws: WebSocket):
    await manager.connect(ws)
    try:
        while True:
            data = await ws.receive_json()
            # data: {"type":"command","text":"Chrome ni och"}
            await manager.handle_message(ws, data)
    except WebSocketDisconnect:
        manager.disconnect(ws)
4.2 websocket_manager.py
connection tracking, broadcast, send structured JSON.

4.3 ai_services.py — interfeys
get_intent_from_ai(text) -> {intent, params, confidence}

tts_generate_audio(text, voice) -> bytes (48kHz PCM or mp3)

stt_transcribe(audio_bytes) -> text

call_tool(tool_name, params) (Tool Calling mapping)

4.4 command_handler.py
handle_command(text, user):

run local IntentParser (regex + keywords). If match → execute local action function.

else call get_intent_from_ai.

Based on intent route to executor or trigger AI response.

On AI response, generate TTS + viseme timing → send via WS with animation_triggers.

