);

CREATE TABLE commands (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  command_text TEXT UNIQUE,
  category TEXT,
  created_at DATETIME
);
10) 40,000 buyruqni yaratish — strategiya va skript (safe, high-quality)
Masala: bir-birini takrorlamaydigan, “haqiqiy” buyruqlar. Yaxshi usul — kategoriyalar + verb + object + modifier qatoridan generatsiya qilish, ammo har bir jumla semantik bo‘lsin.

Approach:

Kategoriya: Chrome, Fayl, Media, System, Terminal, Desktop, Network, DevTools, Editor, Git, DB

Verb list: och, yop, yarat, o‘chirish, nomini o‘zgartir, yukla, ko‘rsat, ijro et, to‘xtat, restart,...

Object list: Documents papkasi, Downloads, index.html, rasm.png, youtube.com, spotify, terminal, VSCode

Modifier: bugungi sana, 50% hajm, background, incognito, sudo bilan, root bilan, admin huquqi bilan, specific path

Skript misoli (Python) — bu avval berilgan skriptdan takomillashtirilgan variant:

python
Copy code
import random, itertools, json
cats = ["Chrome","Fayl","Media","System","Terminal","Network","Editor"]
verbs = ["och","yop","yarat","o‘chirish","nomini o‘zgartir","yukla","ijro et","to‘xtat","restart qil"]
objects = ["Documents papkasidagi fayl","Downloads papkasidagi rasm.png","youtube.com sahifasini","spotify o‘ynash ro‘yxatini"]
mods = ["bugungi sana bilan","20% balandroq hajmda","fon rejimida","incognito rejimida","admin huquqi bilan"]

commands = set()
while len(commands) < 40000:
    c = random.choice(cats)
    v = random.choice(verbs)
    o = random.choice(objects)
    m = random.choice(mods) if random.random() < 0.6 else ""
    cmd = f"{c} da {o} ni {v} {m}".strip()
    commands.add(cmd)

# write to file...
Keyinchalik har bir qatorni semantik tozalash: bosh harf, tinish belgisi, uniq constraint enforced.

Nota Bene: Celebrity persona / voice fayllarini foydalanishda qonuniy va etik ruxsatni tekshirish shart.

